text: The Baojun RS-7 is a midsize crossover produced by Baojun, a marque of SAIC- GM-Wuling. Among Baojun models the RS-7 is considered a flagship, seeing as it is the largest and most expensive vehicle the brand currently sells. Like all Baojun models, its sale is limited to the Chinese market. == References == RS-7 Category:SAIC-GM-Wuling Category:Crossover sport utility vehicles Category:Cars introduced in 2020
